TEXT.TITLE: PAKISTAN TO RETENDER FOR RBD PALM OIL TOMORROW
TEXT.BODY: Pakistan will retender for 6,000 tonnes of refined bleached deodorised palm oil for second half March shipment tomorrow, after failing to take up offers today, palm oil traders said. REUTER
